{"type":"message","id":"c6d19a6e","parentId":"a2537195","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:49:12.649Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6qrqhwp89byh_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"azhua-skill-vetter\ncapability-evolver\njx76-gog\nmiaoda-doc-parse\nmiaoda-image-understanding\nmiaoda-speech-to-text\nmiaoda-text-gen-image\nmiaoda-web-fetch\nmiaoda-web-search\nplaywright\nweda-connector\ndaily-report-review\nfeishu-mail\nfind-skills\ngithub\nself-improving-agent\nskill-creator\nsummarize"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"azhua-skill-vetter\ncapability-evolver\njx76-gog\nmiaoda-doc-parse\nmiaoda-image-understanding\nmiaoda-speech-to-text\nmiaoda-text-gen-image\nmiaoda-web-fetch\nmiaoda-web-search\nplaywright\nweda-connector\ndaily-report-review\nfeishu-mail\nfind-skills\ngithub\nself-improving-agent\nskill-creator\nsummarize","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774644552644}}
{"type":"message","id":"3adc2c6a","parentId":"c6d19a6e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:49:14.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The miaoda-web-search skill is in /home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"9030ce99d01724ebd72ff29dd9497a683093356f539b0eaad185f03d9e9c65a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_br3nnx2rloj0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3162,"output":77,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47220,"cost":{"input":0.0009486,"output":0.0000924,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00236043}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774644552648}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecd5c3c2","parentId":"3adc2c6a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:49:14.951Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_br3nnx2rloj0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774644554931}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0ef5cca","parentId":"ecd5c3c2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:49:17.968Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest information on the relevant industries. Let me search for multiple topics.","thinkingSignature":"6b94ea5a1f96b4b4ae8303e1e906de65dcd11be8a4342fab98af16be69c6f851"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5lveix1fuvjr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新政策 2025 2026 中小企业\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3754,"output":82,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47817,"cost":{"input":0.0011262,"output":0.00009839999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00254403}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774644554944}}
